The following people have contributed to the FDC+ Serial Drive Server codebase:

Joe Toppe <mreppot@gmail.com>
   TypeScript implementation, web interface (Svelte 5 + Tailwind 4),
   MCP server, GPIO LED status indicators, OpenAPI documentation.
   (2024–present)

The FDC+ Enhanced Floppy Disk Controller hardware itself is by Mike Douglas
(deramp.com). It is referenced here but not part of this codebase.
